    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062245_12_3902-3914",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "3902-3914",
      "markText": "她想死，同时想定居巴黎。",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062245&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=3902&rangeEnd=3914",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e35327d0813ab7ed0g015933?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=3902&rangeEnd=3914"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062245_10_1202-1254",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1202-1254",
      "markText": "恰恰相反，一个男人难道不应该无所不知吗？不应该是样样精通，带给你激情的力量、生活的雅致以及所有的奥秘吗？",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062245&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1202&rangeEnd=1254",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e35327d0813ab7ed0g015933?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1202&rangeEnd=1254"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062245_24_5223-5272",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "5223-5272",
      "markText": "人类的话语就像一口裂了缝的锅，当我们在上面拍打出一些旋律企图吸引繁星时，到头来却使得狗熊手舞足蹈。",
      "totalCount": 323,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062245&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=5223&rangeEnd=5272",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e35327d0813ab7ed0g015933?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=5223&rangeEnd=5272"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062245_4_7940-8014",
